{"tid":339021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆先兆】供應創新高未來3至4年私樓供應近10萬！","createTime":"2017-07-28T16:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T15:03:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e918cd65dd26173823121b2c8093491504a4fbd8","tid":339021,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170728/large/1501212219_3b87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170728%2Flarge%2F1501212219_3b87.jpg&h=3cb3c32d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年07月28日<br />\n住宅供應持續創新高。根據運輸及房屋局數據顯示，截至今年6月底，未來3至4年的一手私人住宅供應量預計為9.8萬個單位，按季增加2,000伙，再創政府自2004年9月起每季公佈供應數字以來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n潛在供應中，包括仍未售出的貨尾8,000伙；建築中但仍未售出或未發售的樓花共6.1萬伙，以及2.9萬個隨時可動工的熟地。潛在供應數字增加，因熟地增多2,000伙。<br />\n今年第二季私人住宅施工量約6,000個單位，按季增3,500個單位，升1.4倍。但上半年累計施工量只有8,500個，較去年同期少7,700伙或47.5%。<br />\n而第二季落成量則與首季相若，有4,400伙。上半年合共有8,800個單位落成，按年升18.9%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170728/57011296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170728%2F57011296&d=o1Fh5s5%2FtNpxqMkepdJf%2F8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3870938f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170728%2F57011296&h=1fc7b658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170728/57011296</a>"},{"pid":"2a4caa4740e10fd770072f6cad1b3295cb9fe3ad","tid":339021,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da367cf5715471497ed61d023aa153ee61dae060","tid":339021,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"配合越來越多啲30歲左右嘅人移民，有戲睇"},{"pid":"57e962c207921fbeabfab041a484643d1e40facd","tid"